<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TeamSync</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #161637;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        header .nav-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        header .nav-link:hover {
            color: #548ca9;
        }
        main {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #5e8578af;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .hero .cta-button {
            background-color: #161637;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .hero .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #1a1c3a;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        .how-it-works {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .how-it-works h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .step {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1 1 30%;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .step:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        .step h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .testimonials {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .testimonials h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .testimonial-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .testimonial-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .testimonial-card p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        .contact {
            background-color: #5e8578af;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;

        }
        .contact h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .contact form input,
        .contact form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        .contact form button {
            background-color:#161637;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .contact form button:hover {
            background-color: #161637;
        }
        footer {
            background-color:#161637;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <nav class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center px-6">
            <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">TeamSync</a>
            <div class="flex space-x-8">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
                <a href="#features" class="nav-link">Features</a>
                <a href="#testimonials" class="nav-link">Testimonials</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
                <a href="/login" class="nav-link">Sign In</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>TeamSync: The Future of Team Collaboration</h1>
        <p>Effortlessly manage your team, projects, and deadlines all in one place.</p>
        <button class="cta-button">Get Started</button>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Effortless Scheduling</h3>
            <p>Easily create and manage schedules for your team without any hassle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Real-Time Collaboration</h3>
            <p>Collaborate on projects seamlessly and track progress in real-time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Data Insights</h3>
            <p>Get detailed insights into team productivity and project performance.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 1: Create Your Team</h3>
                <p>Set up your team and define roles, tasks, and responsibilities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 2: Assign Projects</h3>
                <p>Assign projects and deadlines to each team member for seamless coordination.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 3: Track and Collaborate</h3>
                <p>Monitor progress, provide feedback, and collaborate on tasks.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
        <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-cards">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <h3>Emily Roberts</h3>
                <p>"TeamSync has revolutionized how our team collaborates and tracks projects. It's an essential tool for us."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <h3>David Miller</h3>
                <p>"We love the real-time features and how easy it is to keep track of everything in one place."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <h3>Samantha Lee</h3>
                <p>"The user-friendly interface and powerful features make TeamSync the perfect solution for our team."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions? Feel free to reach out to us, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea placeholder="Your Message" rows="4" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 TeamSync. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
